msgid "IC 引脚检测 2D（Lead 2D，AI）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:6
msgid "在引脚阵列上自动生成引脚子框，结合 AI 缺陷检测识别桥接、缺焊、虚焊、少锡等。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:8
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:10
msgid "模板编辑器中绘制对应 ROI 后，在参数面板中配置该工具的参数。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:12
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:14
msgid "**用途**：在引脚阵列上自动生成引脚子框，结合 AI 缺陷检测识别桥接、缺焊、虚焊、少锡等。检测框上的三角箭头指向引脚 *外侧*。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst
msgid "引脚2D(AI)示意"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:20
msgid "**参数说明**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:22
msgid "**引脚数量（Lead Count）**：在 ROI 内自动均分生成对应个数的子 ROI。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:23
msgid "**引脚宽度 (mm)（Lead Width）**：匹配实际引脚宽度，使子 ROI 与实体引脚对齐。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:24
msgid "**引脚角度（Lead Angle）**：引脚相对 ROI 的方向角。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:25
msgid "**引脚阈值（Lead Threshold）**：基于每个引脚子 ROI 的 AI 分数判定缺陷。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:26
msgid "**桥接阈值（Bridge Threshold）**：相邻引脚间连锡（短路）的判定阈值。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:27
msgid ""
"**桥接宽度 (mm)（Bridge Width）/ 间隙宽度 (%)（Gap "
"Width）**：定义相邻引脚间桥接检测带的宽度；可按毫米或按引脚间隙百分比设定，居中裁剪以避免引脚边缘干扰。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:28
msgid ""
"**引脚忽略列表（Lead Ignore List）/ 桥接忽略列表（Bridge Ignore List）**：选择不参与检测的引脚 / "
"桥接（从左到右编号，注意特征框角度）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:29
msgid "**启用可视化（Enable Visualization）**：显示引脚子框与检测结果。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:30
msgid "**使用同步参数（Use sync param）**：开启后，对同一组件下所有同类型引脚特征共用一套参数；关闭后可对单个特征单独调参。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst
msgid "引脚2D AI检测示意"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:37
msgid "**常见问题与提示**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:41
msgid "**引脚末端误报多**：若元件末端没有红色焊料，关闭 **引脚末端** 子检测。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:42
msgid "**焊盘检测误报多**：焊盘检测把红色作为有效区域；若元件引脚没有明显焊盘区域，关闭 **焊盘** 子检测。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:43
msgid "**短引脚定位不准**：使用 **短引脚模式**，整段引脚作为一个检测区域，定位更稳定。"
msgstr ""

